steps.html_instructions: Head southwest on S Euclid Ave toward E Pleasant Dr
S Euclid Ave turns right and becomes E Pleasant Dr
Turn left onto S Pierre St

Take the 1st right onto US-83 S/W Sioux Ave
Continue to follow US-83 S

Turn right to merge onto I-90 W/US-83 S
Continue to follow I-90 W
Take exit 150 for S Dakota 73 S toward Kadoka
Turn left onto SD-73 N

Turn right onto SD-73 S/US-18 W
Continue to follow US-18 W

Turn left onto SD-391
Entering Nebraska
Continue onto NE-27 S
Turn right onto US-20 W/Bridges to Buttes Byway
Turn left onto NE-87 S

Turn right onto E 25th St/Nance Rd
Continue to follow Nance Rd

Turn left onto NE-2 E/US-385 S
Continue to follow US-385 S
Turn right onto NE-62A
Continue onto US-26 W

Turn left onto NE-71 S/NE-92 S
Continue to follow NE-71 S

Turn right onto NE-88 E
Entering Wyoming
Continue onto WY-151 W
Turn left onto US-85 S

Keep left at the fork, follow signs for Interstate 25 S/U.S. 85 S/U.S. 87 S/Cheyenne and merge onto I-25 S/US-85 S/US-87 S
Continue to follow I-25 S/US-87 S
Take exit 11 for Randall Ave toward Pershing Blvd
Turn left onto Randall Ave (signs for Pershing Blvd)
Slight right onto Pioneer Ave

Take the 3rd left onto W 24th St
Destination will be on the left
